    "Third, there is a possibility that ChatGPT may provide biased information or information that is not relevant (Hu et al., 2023).",
    "ChatGPT mediated knowledge management system will be able to check ChatGPT information in the context of organizational requirements by correlating both knowledge bases.",
    "Thus, it has the potential to nullify the biases and ensure the relevancy and usefulness of the information.",
    "Fourth, soft knowledge management issues such as commitment, recognition, attitudes, perceptions, and assumptions about the role of technology in knowledge management are also concerns to address for technology-mediated social interaction (Sanzogni et al., 2017).",
    "ChatGPT mediated knowledge management system provides employees with a social interaction platform through its robust"
  ]
